    "Management": {
      "text": "Immobilize cervical spine for suspected trauma\nFluid resuscitation\n20 mL/kg x3 as needed; start pressors thereafter\nAntibiotics\nfor\nsepsis\nor\nmeningitis\n(consider\nantiviral\nit patient is toxic)\nNaloxone\nfor\nopioid\nor\nclonidine overdose\n(0.01-0.1mg/kg IV q2 min)\nGlucose\nfor\nhypoglycemia\n(2 mL/kg of 25% dextrose)\nAvoid\nsodium bicarbonate\nfor\nmetabolic acidosis\nunless pH <7.0\nControl\nseizures\nPrevent\nhypothermia\n, treat\nhyperthermia",
